        <mxCell id="erd_note" value="CHANGES from the server-push design:&#xa;• push_subscriptions table DROPPED (no server push in v1).&#xa;• reminder_settings: dropped last_sent_at + its own timezone snapshot;&#xa;  profiles.timezone is the single canonical zone.&#xa;• reminder_settings.updated_at is the re-arm signal — clients re-read &amp;&#xa;  re-schedule when it changes. A tz-change trigger touches it too.&#xa;• RLS owner-only (auth.uid()=user_id) on every table; canonical ml; totals AT TIME ZONE." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;spacing=8;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="850" y="70" width="410" height="175" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
